{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"ec84b30c62","title":"对中南局关于近几个月内少开主要干部出席的业务会议的建议的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"3533fbda59","index":1,"year":1952,"month":1,"day":11,"articleId":"ec84b30c62"},{"id":"c4d2d12635","index":0,"year":1952,"month":1,"day":8,"articleId":"ec84b30c62"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji31","name":"毛泽东全集第31卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/31-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji31":{"comments":[{"id":"a54d46e621","publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"ec84b30c62","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"这是毛泽东对中共济南市委关于开展三反运动部署的报告的批语。该报告的主要特点，一是内容全面充实，既拒要列举了各行各业暴露出的贪污浪费官停主义现象，说明开展“三反”运动之有的放失，又明确提出了从机关到企业到警备部队方方面面开展运动的部署要求；二是提出运动的重点是清贪污分子特别是大贪污犯，抓住了运动的要害：三是开展运动的决心大，方法对，要求各级领导亲自动手，放手发动群众，务求达到目的，不获全胜决不收兵。"}],"contents":[{"id":"bc9a7f44fa","type":"title","text":"对中共济南市委报告的批示则","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"ec84b30c62"},{"id":"a54d46e621","type":"paragraph","text":"客中央局，并转分局、省市区党委：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"ec84b30c62"},{"id":"d6f92f3c8f","type":"paragraph","text":"济南市委这个报告很好，请转发各大城市参考，并在党刊上发表。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"ec84b30c62"},{"id":"1db7712efc","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"ec84b30c62"},{"id":"491b999799","type":"paragraph","text":"一月六日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"ec84b30c62"}],"page":{"id":"3f9b752dc7","publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"ec84b30c62","start":245,"end":245}}}},"__N_SSG":true}